{
  "stem": "1753.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they put that whole family tree together the best they could put it together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no, nothing in particular, just going back to-- to the Kort family in the 15th century, and so on, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is a book that was published.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's-- incidentally, that's a company in Ohio that does things like that, relating to rare names in America.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how that family tree came about.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in fact, they even researched and they-- they came up with the coat of arms that our ancestors used, and I have it--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in my study here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they all--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Except for one grandmother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Except for that one grandmother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I remember, you know, I-- while I was born in Leipzig, when I was still very young-- and of course, as I pointed out before and will point out again, I had a brother and a sister-- that when we-- when we were all still very small children, we moved to a little village by the name [NON-ENGLISH], near Heidelberg in southern Germany.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to school there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was a very small Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my parents wanted me, especially-- because my brother and my sister, they're each two years older than I.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the oldest was my sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my brother was two years older than I.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they already started to learn a trade in some other cities in Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my parents wanted me to be with a larger Jewish community, so they sent me to a town near the Swiss and French border by the name of Breisach.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a relatively large Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
